snippet.title: Jack of Clubs: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3057820/Jack_of_Clubs/

Play golf, fight robots, and explore an 18-hole course as Jack, a pilot stranded on a recently-abandoned island resort. Discover secrets and complete challenges to earn items that improve your golf game. Unravel the mystery of the island in pursuit of your golf ball across a huge, continuous course.

Release date: November 21, 2024
Demo release date: October 7, 2024
